And the aforesaid Edmund Brudenel seeks judgment for our Lord the King, because the matter above alleged by the aforesaid Richard and Joan is not a sufficient answer in law against the presentments aforesaid and the matter alleged against them on behalf of our Lord the King, and that the aforesaid wear and all the aforesaid nuisance be removed and wholly thrown down.
